6
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:45,970
Back then,

7
00:00:46,390 --> 00:00:48,140
the Crown Prince falsely accused

8
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,730
Mr. Xia'an

9
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,730
of conspiring with the enemy country

10
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:54,540
through letters.

11
00:00:54,710 --> 00:00:56,690
I'll take the responsibility
to gather evidence

12
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:59,050
to clear Mr. Xia'an's name.

13
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,970
I humbly request

14
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,250
