Fragrant sachets for sale!

21
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,730
Fragrant sachets for sale!

22
00:01:33,790 --> 00:01:35,530
The Xia'an clan

23
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,450
is indeed meticulous and bold.

24
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,300
They have been hiding

25
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,420
in this marketplace of the capital
over the years.

26
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,069
This is a safe

27
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:44,300
hiding place.

28
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:47,170
I've been here since I was a kid.

29
00:01:48,790 --> 00:01:51,010
