30
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,559
Look,

31
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,239
Madam Liu makes the best sugarplums.

32
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,119
Later,

33
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,730
I'll buy some for you.

34
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:39,770
Hurry.

35
00:02:40,350 --> 00:02:41,160
Coming.

36
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,610
Look over there.

37
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:50,210
There's a rouge store.

38
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:52,860
The seller is a man.

39
