is actually run by Mrs. Zhao.

44
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,380
I don't even

45
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,420
have a chance to be whipped.

46
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:32,799
Shall we try it?

47
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,990
Really? Let's go.

48
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:36,170
Excuse me!

