To achieve your goal,

57
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:49,930
first,

58
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:52,170
be honest with your desires.

59
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,930
Second,

60
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,860
don't compromise.

61
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:00,420
(On the day when you were injured,)

62
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,900
(you asked me)

63
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,730
(if I liked you.)

64
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,860
(I can tell you the answer now.)

65
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,980
(First Young Master,)

66
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:11,420
(I do like you.)

67
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:13,050
(Even so,)

68
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,050
(there's nothing I can do.)

69
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,660
(You're going to be the prince consort)

70
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,220
(and have a bright future)

71
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,810
(in the imperial court.)

72
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,490
(I don't want to hold you back.)

73
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:34,080
♪Maybe by hiding my heart♪

74
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:39,139
♪I can escape from your sight♪

75
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:42,059
♪Lying to you that my love for you♪

76
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:48,040
♪Is only one ten-thousandth♪

77
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:57,340
What did you just say?

78
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,930
You want to break off the engagement?

79
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:02,900
I'm no longer the legitimate elder son
of the General's Residence.

80
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:04,980
I don't deserve Her Highness.

81
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:09,780
I always dote on my sister.

82
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:12,050
Now that you've broken her heart,

83
00:06:13,190 --> 00:06:14,810
do you think I'll let you off?

84
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:18,860
I made this decision

85
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,340
after considering from your angle,
Your Highness.

86
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:24,170
If I were to marry Her Highness,

87
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,050
I'm afraid you might become the target

88
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:28,420
of malicious speculations
in the imperial court.

89
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,930
Who do you think you are, Xiao Yeting?

90
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:47,020
You want to break off the engagement?

91
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,780
No, I'll break off the engagement.

92
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,130
I don't want you!

93
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,900
Ban Meng,

94
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:15,810
I'll tear you apart!

95
00:07:51,277 --> 00:07:52,977
(Great Virtues Endure)
Xiao Yeting,

96
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,660
I've treated you like my own son.

97
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:58,039
I can't believe you would frame me

98
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,860
for your personal fame and gain.

99
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,919
Do you think

100
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,300
the Crown Prince will value you then?

101
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,170
You're a traitor!

102
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,100
Scoundrel!

103
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:10,220
Godfather,

104
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:13,420
concerning our deep bond,

105
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:16,900
I'll give you a quick death.

106
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,810
Xiao Yeting,

107
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:21,900
you failed my daughter.

108
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,980
Burn it down.

109
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,540
(Godfather,)

110
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,500
(over these years,)

111
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:42,749
(I've tried means and ways)

112
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,690
(to make myself stronger)

113
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:48,200
(so that I'm powerful enough
to fight against the Crown Prince)

114
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:50,780
(and demand justice
for the Xia'an clan.)

115
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:54,380
(I only found out
that Le was still alive.)

116
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,570
(For the rest of my life,)

117
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:58,319
(For the rest of my life,
I'll protect her)

118
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,540
(even at the cost of my safety.)

119
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:08,440
(Great Virtues Endure)

120
00:09:32,549 --> 00:09:33,850
Yanping?

121
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:36,620
Are you surprised

122
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,050
why I'm here?

123
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:42,330
Because I know you well.

124
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:50,780
Whenever you feel down,

125
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:56,850
you'd come here
to pay your respects to these traitors

126
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:59,500
and mourn your Xia'an Le.

127
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:01,540
Don't call them traitors.

128
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,380
We both know

129
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,540
it was the Crown Prince
who framed Mr. Xia'an.

130
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,660
Don't think I don't know

131
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,170
you pledged your loyalty

132
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:18,500
to my brother

133
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,570
and betrayed Xia'an

134
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:24,090
because you realized

135
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,570
the Xia'an clan was past help.

136
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,210
Back then,

137
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,420
you planned

138
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,050
to secretly keep Xia'an Le alive

139
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,669
while you handled

140
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:37,210
the Xia'an Clan, didn't you?

141
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,660
How did you know about that?

142
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,780
Were you behind

143
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,810
Le's death?

144
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,050
Did you set
the Xia'an Residence on fire?

145
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,330
Yeting.

146
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,450
What are you trying to do?

147
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,660
Answer me.

148
00:11:04,068 --> 00:11:07,008
You're the man I chose.

149
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,839
I couldn't allow

150
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,999
your fiancee to live

151
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,660
in this world.

152
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,970
You must hate me now.

153
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:20,140
I hate myself, too.

154
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:24,050
I was too young

155
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:27,789
to understand that the living

156
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:29,500
can never compete with the dead.

157
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,620
Even though we're engaged,

158
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,810
I know

159
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:38,170
