160
00:11:39,910 --> 00:11:42,090
I learned my lesson this time.

161
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,850
I didn't plan to kill Ban Meng.

162
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,300
I only used a little trick

163
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,620
to let you fall out of love with her.

164
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,540
It's your fault.

165
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:03,140
You actually break off the engagement

166
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:08,090
because of Ban Meng.

167
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,500
Xiao Yeting, it's you
who brings harm upon her!

168
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,140
What's that supposed to mean, Yanping?

169
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,690
What did you do to Ban Meng?

170
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,450
What did you do to her?

171
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,330
Tell me!

172
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:45,620
As of now, she should be...

173
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:51,210
I want to completely remove her

174
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:54,260
from your heart.

175
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,690
I left something there.

176
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,210
I'll fetch it for you.

177
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,420
Hyah!

178
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:22,050
- Hyah!
- Hyah!

179
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,319
What's going on?

180
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,260
Hyah!

181
00:13:28,620 --> 00:13:29,430
Be careful.

