♪I'm leaning on you♪

187
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:46,640
♪For a moment♪

188
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:49,040
♪Of refuge♪

189
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:53,899
♪I'm afraid that if my beautiful dream♪

190
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,840
♪Fades away♪

191
00:13:56,180 --> 00:14:00,419
♪I'll wake up♪

192
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:08,160
♪Alone in a long silence♪

193
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:12,339
♪To love or to hate♪

194
00:14:12,340 --> 00:14:14,779
♪I can't help it♪

195
